Kenya is building more than just a stadium.
Talanta Stadium represents ambition, identity, and Kenya’s push onto the global sports and entertainment stage.

In this documentary trailer, we take you inside one of the country’s most ambitious infrastructure projects – exploring the vision behind Talanta Stadium, its design, its impact on sports development, and what it means for Kenya’s future. From architecture to national pride, from youth talent to global recognition, this is a story of a nation daring to dream bigger.

Is Talanta Stadium the project that will redefine Kenya’s sporting legacy?
